Description: Cross-platform audio capture tool
 A robust, high-performance audio capture tool for recording
 system and application-specific audio on Windows, macOS, and Linux.
 .
 Features:
  * Cross-platform support (Windows, macOS, Linux)
  * System-wide audio capture
  * Application-specific audio capture (Windows and Linux)
  * Multiple output formats (WAV, RAW PCM)
  * Configurable audio quality parameters
  * Interactive and command-line modes 